snippet.title: Prehistoric Kingdom | Update 10 Trailer
snippet.description:
Update 10 is coming soon on February 26! Introducing 4 new species, an expanded boreal biome, and the Stone Age building set, the park has never looked so prehistoric.

Buy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/666150/Prehistoric_Kingdom/
Buy on Epic Games: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/prehistoric-kingdom

Take control of limitless power in Prehistoric Kingdom to build, manage and grow the ultimate zoo for extinct animals - available for $29.99 USD.
